<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
    
<%- include('partials/Navbar') %>

    
  <!-- Hero Slider -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-slide active">
        <img src="images/bn2.webp" alt="Slide 1" onerror="this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/1200x600/083d5d/FFFFFF?text=Slide+1'">    
    </div>
    <div class="hero-slide">
        <img src="images/bn1.webp" alt="Slide 2" onerror="this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/1200x600/4da8da/FFFFFF?text=Slide+2'">
    </div>
    <div class="hero-slide">
        <img src="images/bn3.webp" alt="Slide 3" onerror="this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/1200x600/ff6b35/FFFFFF?text=Slide+3'">
    </div>
    <div class="hero-slide">
        <img src="images/bn4.png" alt="Slide 4" onerror="this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/1200x600/085d0f/FFFFFF?text=Slide+4'">
    </div>
    
    <button class="hero-nav hero-nav-prev">
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-left"></i>
    </button>
    <button class="hero-nav hero-nav-next">
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i>
    </button>
    
    <div class="hero-controls">
        <button class="control-btn play-pause-btn active" title="Pause Auto-Play">
            <i class="fas fa-pause"></i>
        </button>
        <div class="slide-counter">
            <span class="current-slide"></span>  <span class="total-slides"></span>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="hero-dots">
        <span class="hero-dot active" data-slide="0">
            <span class="hero-dot-progress"></span>
        </span>
        <span class="hero-dot" data-slide="1">
            <span class="hero-dot-progress"></span>
        </span>
        <span class="hero-dot" data-slide="2">
            <span class="hero-dot-progress"></span>
        </span>
        <span class="hero-dot" data-slide="3">
            <span class="hero-dot-progress"></span>
        </span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- NEW MIDDLE SECTION - EXCELLENCE SECTION -->
  <section class="excellence-section">
    <div class="container">
      <!-- Section Header -->
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="subtitle">Excellence in Pharmacy Education</span><br>
        <h2>Beyond the Classroom</h2>
        <p>At Maa Maturani Devi Pharmacy College, we believe in nurturing well-rounded professionals through academic excellence, holistic development, and industry-ready training.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature Cards with Images -->
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="card-image">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1532094349884-543bc11b234d?w=600&h=400&fit=crop" alt="Pharmacy Lab">
            <div class="card-overlay">
              <i class="fas fa-microscope"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h3>Academic Excellence</h3>
            <p>State-of-the-art laboratories and digital library with experienced faculty ensuring outstanding university results.</p>
            <ul class="feature-list">
              <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Well-equipped Pharma Labs</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Digital Library with 5000+ Journals</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Research & Innovation Center</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> 95% University Exam Success Rate</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="card-image">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1524178232363-1fb2b075b655?w=600&h=400&fit=crop" alt="Students Playing Sports">
            <div class="card-overlay">
              <i class="fas fa-futbol"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h3>Holistic Development</h3>
            <p>Beyond academics, we nurture well-rounded personalities through sports, cultural activities, and a supportive campus environment.</p>
            <ul class="feature-list">
              <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Annual Sports Meet & Tournaments</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Cultural & Technical Fests</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Ragging-Free Campus Environment</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Student Clubs & Associations</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="card-image">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1521791136064-7986c2920216?w=600&h=400&fit=crop" alt="Placement Session">
            <div class="card-overlay">
              <i class="fas fa-briefcase"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h3>Career & Placement Support</h3>
            <p>Dedicated training and placement cell to bridge the gap between academia and industry requirements.</p>
            <ul class="feature-list">
              <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> 100% Placement Assistance</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Industrial Visits & Internships</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Job Counseling & Resume Building</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Mock Interviews & Soft Skills Training</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Gallery Section -->
      <div class="gallery-section">
        <h3>Campus Life & Moments</h3>
        <div class="gallery-grid">
          <div class="gallery-item">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523240795612-9a054b0db644?w=600&h=400&fit=crop" alt="Lab Session">
            <div class="gallery-caption">Hands-on Lab Training</div>
          </div>
          <div class="gallery-item">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517649763962-0c623066013b?w=600&h=400&fit=crop" alt="Sports Day">
            <div class="gallery-caption">Annual Sports Meet 2024</div>
          </div>
          <div class="gallery-item">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1564069114553-7215e1ff1890?w=600&h=400&fit=crop" alt="Industrial Visit">
            <div class="gallery-caption">Industrial Visit to Pharma Company</div>
          </div>
          <div class="gallery-item">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511632765486-a01980e01a18?w=600&h=400&fit=crop" alt="Cultural Event">
            <div class="gallery-caption">Cultural Celebration - Freshers 2024</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonials Section -->
      <div class="testimonials-section">
        <h3>Student Voices</h3>
        <div class="testimonials-grid">
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="testimonial-img">
              <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/44.jpg" alt="Student">
            </div>
            <i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i>
            <p>"The supportive faculty and excellent lab facilities at MMD Pharmacy College helped me build a strong foundation in pharmaceutical sciences. The placement assistance was invaluable."</p>
            <h4>Priya Sharma</h4>
            <span>B.Pharma Final Year | Placed at Sun Pharma</span>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="testimonial-img">
              <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/32.jpg" alt="Student">
            </div>
            <i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i>
            <p>"Beyond academics, the sports events and cultural fests made my college life memorable. The ragging-free environment made me feel safe and focused on learning."</p>
            <h4>Rahul Verma</h4>
            <span>D.Pharma Graduate 2024</span>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="testimonial-img">
              <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/68.jpg" alt="Student">
            </div>
            <i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i>
            <p>"The industry visits and guest lectures from pharma experts gave us real-world exposure. The placement cell's support helped me crack interviews with top companies."</p>
            <h4>Anjali Singh</h4>
            <span>B.Pharma 2023 | Research Associate</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

     
  </section>

  <script src="js/slide.js"></script>


  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>